awards.text: Won 1 Golden Globe. Another 2 wins & 3 nominations.

fullplot: An awkward young Irish farm girl Kate Brady moves to Dublin and shares a room with funny, outgoing Baba Brennan, where she soon meets Eugene Gaillard, a middle-aged writer, who is immediately attracted to the shy and innocent Kate, ignoring the more sophisticated Baba.
plot: In 1960s Dublin a young girl becomes involved with an older man, a much-travelled and still married land-owner.
title: Girl with Green Eyes
